            <ns0:div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <ns0:p>?((staurogram)) Pontius lived in pace more or less 80 years. He departed 16 days before the Kalends of June in the consulate of Opilio, vir clarissimus, in the second indiction.</ns0:p>
            </ns0:div>
            <ns0:div type="translation" xml:lang="it" resp="ISegesta">
                <ns0:p>((staurogramma)) Pontius &#232; vissuto in pace pi&#249; o meno ottant'anni. &#200; morto il 24 maggio (nell'anno del) consolato del vir clarissimus Opilio, II dell'indizione</ns0:p>
            </ns0:div>
            <ns0:div type="commentary">
                <ns0:p>The only funerary inscription to date from Segesta, this provides important evidence for the continuity of settlement in Segesta in the sixth century CE in the period of the Gothic domination.</ns0:p>
            </ns0:div>
